        "TileImage": "$($repository 87ab7e2c-cdae-4566-b32e-75bc9cea84fd).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening, Lisa. Your targets are four businessmen who made a fortune drowning others in debt. Poetic justice demands a swim. Theron, Dale, and Frank will find that the water’s less forgiving than their lawyers. As for Charles Blake III, the brains of the bunch—he’ll sip on success one last time… with a toxic twist. Make it quiet, 47. Let irony do the talking.",
